{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we were sleeping in the tents, our hair would even sort of freeze to the tent, you know, because we were so close.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the middle was the stove.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in the morning when we would get up, we would stand around the little stove to get dressed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what were you wearing?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by that time, see, until our shoes, our own shoes lasted, we wore them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that, we were given whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we were in Torun already, we were given the wooden shoes and dresses which used to be what they collected in Auschwitz or whatever, because we didn't have a uniform.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were wearing those dresses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some had a coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some had rags.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to put rags around our feet and our legs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those wooden shoes were big, so we were able to put rags.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what we were wearing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the 15-- out of the 1,500 of us, slowly, about 700 or 800 died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean naturally, without being shot or killed, but they were so weak already that they died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, I think it was by trucks, as far as I could remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- there, we had the SS soldiers guarding us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- we had-- like, the camp had one officer who was called the oberscharfuhrer, who was, like, over us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, if the SS wanted something, they would have to communicate with the oberscharfuhrer to get us to do this or that or the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they would be watching us so we don't want to escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or we-- certain things that nobody communicates with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there was a mother and daughter who-- she befriended one of the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
